{"calories":"730","carbs":100,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"Everyone loves risotto, but the labor-intensive, stand-at-stove method often required? Not so much. Luckily, we’ve created a hands-off simmering method for risotto, which makes for the same supremely creamy results, with way less effort. This version combines cremini, shiitake, and oyster mushrooms, folded into Arborio rice along with peas, Parmesan, and a little porcini mushroom broth. Crispy Parmesan fricos on top add a crunchy element to this elegant yet comforting meal.","difficulty":"medium","external_id":"4204df9753","fat":24,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33845/OfcfwrTRGNCLa7QUfuQU_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0002___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33845/menu_small_OfcfwrTRGNCLa7QUfuQU_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0002___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33843/8qCfslSMRB2ZkqtkfUyP_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0006___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33843/hero_8qCfslSMRB2ZkqtkfUyP_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0006___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33843/menu_small_8qCfslSMRB2ZkqtkfUyP_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0006___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33843/small_square_8qCfslSMRB2ZkqtkfUyP_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0006___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33843/medium_square_8qCfslSMRB2ZkqtkfUyP_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0006___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33843/recipe_profile_page_8qCfslSMRB2ZkqtkfUyP_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0006___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33844/KogAx9KSnS5qcbxWoiQo_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0014___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/33846/large_cropped_UyZlGGjZTsuDUDgmQh6x_Mushroom_Risotto_with_Truffled_Parmesan_Frico___0006___MAIN.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Mushroom Risotto with Truffled Parmesan Frico","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"45-55","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":23,"public_slug":"mushroom-risotto-with-truffle-sage-frico","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/19303/recipe_card20171030-4-13sv002.pdf","recipe_id":3354,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Mushroom Risotto","subtitle":"with Truffled Parmesan Frico","title":"Mushroom Risotto","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eDon't rinse mushrooms, or they'll absorb water and won't brown well during roasting.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eHow to use the remaining truffle zest? Mix with kosher salt and sprinkle over avocado toast.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eCarefully lift the fragile frico off the parchment, but if it breaks, don't worry! It'll get crumbled anyway.\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["baking sheet","2 8\" medium pots, 1 with lid"],"id":3354,"ingredients":["sage","yellow onion","garlic","vegetable stock","porcini mushroom powder","unsalted butter","Arborio rice","white wine","grated Parmesan cheese","truffle zest","peas","parchment paper","shiitake mushrooms","cremini mushrooms","oyster mushrooms"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"sage","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1277/medium_square_medium_square_sage-2.jpg"},{"name":"yellow onion","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/27/medium_square_yellow-onion-test.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"vegetable stock","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/906/medium_square_medium_square_medium_square_beef-broth.jpg"},{"name":"porcini mushroom powder","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/548/medium_square_mushroom_powder.jpg"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/619/medium_square_dairy-butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"Arborio rice","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/322/medium_square_rice-arborio.jpg"},{"name":"white wine","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/256/medium_square_WHITE_WINE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/22/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"},{"name":"truffle zest","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1661/medium_square_truffle_zest.jpg"},{"name":"peas","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/31/medium_square_green-peas.jpg"},{"name":"parchment paper","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/203/medium_square_paper-parchment.jpg"},{"name":"shiitake mushrooms","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/221/medium_square_shiitake-mushrooms-test.jpg"},{"name":"cremini mushrooms","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/326/medium_square_cremini-mushrooms-test2.jpg"},{"name":"oyster mushrooms","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/609/medium_square_oyster-mushrooms.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":16,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":17,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":18,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/29078/recipe_card_size_zBpUTsUqQUKxJ6n2GQf6_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Pick \u003cstrong\u003e1 sage leaf\u003c/strong\u003e, roughly chop, and place in a small bowl; reserve \u003cstrong\u003eremaining whole sage sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e for infusing the risotto in Step 4. Remove and discard \u003cstrong\u003emushroom\u003c/strong\u003e stems, then wipe \u003cstrong\u003ecaps\u003c/strong\u003e clean with a damp paper towel and thinly slice (see Recipe Tip). Peel \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e and cut into small dice. Mince \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast Mushrooms and Make Porcini Broth","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/29079/recipe_card_size_ctXA3iquTsmbQxGYuxGl_2._Roast_Mushrooms_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOn a baking sheet, toss \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e with \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and\u003cstrong\u003e pepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Arrange in a single layer and roast until tender, 12-14 minutes. Meanwhile, in a medium pot, combine \u003cstrong\u003evegetable\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003estock\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003cstrong\u003e porcini mushroom powder\u003c/strong\u003e, and\u003cstrong\u003e 1.5 cups water\u003c/strong\u003e, and bring to a boil over high heat. Then, remove pot from heat and cover to keep warm until Step 4.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Toast Rice","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/29080/recipe_card_size_TA74FDFpSEOsSxPVE3qg_3._Toast_Rice.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e in a separate medium pot over medium heat. When butter is foamy, add \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring, until softening, 5 minutes. Increase heat to medium high and add \u003cstrong\u003erice\u003c/strong\u003e. Cook, stirring frequently, until toasted and translucent, 2-3 minutes (toasting the rice makes for a deliciously nutty flavor and prevents it from absorbing liquid too quickly).\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Simmer Rice","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/29081/recipe_card_size_Ds4XoHpaSYGZsH0LEaaM_4._Cook_Rice.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eReduce heat under pot with rice to medium, and stir in \u003cstrong\u003ewhite wine\u003c/strong\u003e. Simmer until liquid is mostly absorbed, 1-2 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003ereserved sage sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eporcini broth\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e. Increase heat to high and bring to a boil, then reduce heat to medium low and simmer, stirring occasionally, until liquid is mostly absorbed and rice is tender, 15-18 minutes more.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Bake Parmesan Frico","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/29082/recipe_card_size_XAibRoYHSraZ89EckitR_5._Frico.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOnce roasted, transfer \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e to a plate, then line baking sheet with \u003cstrong\u003eparchment paper\u003c/strong\u003e. Add \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etruffle zest\u003c/strong\u003e to bowl with chopped sage, and mix to combine (see Recipe Tip). Pour onto prepared baking sheet and spread in an even circle, about .125-inch thick. Bake until golden and crisp, 2-3 minutes. Then, remove sheet from oven, and using a spatula, loosen \u003cstrong\u003efrico\u003c/strong\u003e from parchment (see Recipe Tip). Set aside.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Finish and Plate Risotto","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/29083/recipe_card_size_MKSP4c6RmKkit6LaiRzw_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOnce rice is tender, remove and discard \u003cstrong\u003esage sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003epeas\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eroasted mushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eremaining butter\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e to combine. Divide \u003cstrong\u003emushroom risotto\u003c/strong\u003e between roomy serving bowls, and crumble \u003cstrong\u003etruffled Parmesan frico\u003c/strong\u003e over top. Enjoy!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Loose Grain","slug":"loose-grain","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}